1817
02:23:02,247 --> 02:23:05,247
"...we collect garbage and
pray somebody confesses."

1818
02:23:06,247 --> 02:23:07,247
They behave badly,

1819
02:23:09,247 --> 02:23:10,747
...they lose fights,

1820
02:23:13,247 --> 02:23:14,747
