1821
02:23:19,747 --> 02:23:21,747
...they die.

1822
02:23:26,747 --> 02:23:29,746
During the youth gang
hysteria of the eighties,

1823
02:23:29,747 --> 02:23:32,747
...the stoically heroic
cop made a comeback,

1824
02:23:33,247 --> 02:23:36,747
