02:29:29,747 --> 02:29:32,747
"...Compton, Pomona, Glendale..."

1895
02:29:33,747 --> 02:29:35,246
"...American suburbia..."

1896
02:29:35,247 --> 02:29:37,747
"...the names you hear about
on the freeway reports."

1897
02:29:39,747 --> 02:29:41,246
